[4.470825, "i", "panda --prompt 'You need to transcribe speech to text.\n\nHere is an audio file /app/audio.mp3\n\nYour task is to recognize the content in the audio file and transcribe it to text.\nYou need to save the recognized text in the /app/output.txt file.\n  - demonstration of the format of /app/output.txt: cool, this is a good task.\n\nHint:\n  - you can use any tools or open-source models on GitHub \\\n  but you need to set up by yourself.\n  - you only have CPUs.'; tmux wait -S done\r"]
